b08f85ddbb23cbf","date":"2026-02-04 10:02:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_05bfeee1.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AI科技大本营","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":99,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_c347f932","title":"文本生成图像模型训练设计：消融实验的经验教训","link":"https://huggingface.co/blog/Photoroom/prx-part2","date":"2026-02-03 11:25:53","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c347f932.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Hugging Face Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_6dbd507b","title":"今日开源（2026-2-2）：阶跃智能 Step-3.5-Flash 系列上线，199B 基座+FP8/Int4 量化技术，压缩优化赋能低开销多硬件 NLP 部署","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501528&idx=1&sn=d4a1cacb26e74cdf45aa3055ca563728","date":"2026-02-02 10:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_6dbd507b.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心SOTA模型","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_01bf1916","title":"LinkedIn 利用 GitHub Actions、CodeQL 和 Semgrep 进行代码扫描","link":"https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/02/linkedin-redesigns-sast-pipeline/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-06 15:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"LinkedIn 通过 GitHub Actions 集成了 CodeQL 和 Semgrep，并利用“存根工作流”架构实现了可扩展、一致且对开发者友好的安全强制执行，从而实现了 SAST 流水线的现代化。","summary":"LinkedIn 重新设计了其静态应用安全测试（SAST）流水线，以克服碎片化、多仓库环境带来的挑战。新架构利用 GitHub Actions 编排 CodeQL 进行深度分析，并使用 Semgrep 进行快速的基于模式的扫描。一项关键创新是在各个仓库中使用“存根工作流（stub workflows）”，将其委托给集中管理的工作流，从而实现即时的全局更新，并绕过 GitHub 原生强制工作流的限制。该系统通过仓库规则集强制执行安全标准，同时通过“终止开关”和自动回退机制维持开发效率，防止流水线故障阻塞合并。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_01bf1916.json","topicTag":"devops","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_cb5b6f84","title":"将 Swift 从应用扩展到服务","link":"https://www.infoq.com/presentations/swift-apps-services/?utm_campaign=infoq_conte